# Conversational AI Chatbot

This repository contains a Conversational AI chatbot built using GPT-like language models. The chatbot provides intelligent responses based on natural language input. You can customize this application to use APIs like OpenAI's GPT models or other NLP frameworks.

## Features:
- Text-based conversational interface
- Chatbot responds with context-aware replies
- API integration for GPT-like models
- Interactive web interface for demo purposes

## Requirements:
- Python 3.x
- Flask
- OpenAI API (or another language model API)
